    "date": "2021-12-08T21:58:32Z",
    "text": "Lead Elimination and Data Guidance Act or the LEAD Guidance Act\n\nThis bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to develop guidance to help public water systems identify high-risk locations for purposes of (1) testing the concentration of lead in drinking water, and (2) replacing lead service lines. High-risk locations are areas that contain an environmental justice community and that are likely to have lead service lines."
  },
